body: *Chief kiss* Beautiful art for the cutest onee-chan, this is the best Ibuki doujinshi out there.
brilliant. still wondering why there is so little hentai doujins of ibuki, she's just a perfect material for that.
Already can't wait for the translation. But why do all the artists forget or ignore her tail? Still a great doujin though. Really looking forward to rolling for her on NA.
